ass="t m0 x9 h4 yfc ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">不依人。<span class="_ _6"></span>表面上看来善知识是人，<span class="_ _6"></span>好像不能依止，<span class="_ _6"></span>但实际上</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfd ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">不是这个意思。 </div><div class="t m0 x1f h4 y1c1 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls27 ws0">藏地的麦彭仁波切，曾造过一部论典叫《解义慧剑》<span class="_ _8"></span><span class="ls0">，</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y141 ffc fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">我以前也翻译过，里面对“四依”就讲得比较清楚。其实，</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
